title: 2009 04-15b Democracy Now!
description:
Amy Goodman
Democracy Now!

JOE BLOW GO AWAY
================

These uploads are done mainly as a courtesy for those of us in the Memphis area who miss our short-lived progressive talk station WWTQ AM680.

For those who want higher quality audio, complete bumper music, immediate uploads of the most current shows, etc... SUBSCRIBE TO THE PODCASTS! Website addresses and daily program offerings are embedded in the mp3 file for each show.

PROGRAMMING NOTE
I will be away from my PC April 24 - April 29. My streamrippers and podcast catchers are set up to capture all the shows, but they won't be posted until April 29/30. I AM NOT DISAPPEARING - JUST VISITING RELATIVES!!
